<header class="content">
<div class="title">
<h2 class="headline h3" itemprop="headline">
<a href="#literature/2013/munro/facts/">
Alice Munro dies aged 92 </a>
</h2>
</div>
</header>
<div class="text">
Canadian author Alice Munro passed away on 15 May 2024. She was awarded the Nobel Prize in Literature 2013 with the motivation “master of the contemporary short story”.<br><a href="#economic-sciences/2002/kahneman/biographical/"><br></a><a href="#literature/2013/munro/biographical/">Biography</a><br> </div>
</div>
